cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.MM

This paper deals with the optimization of wireless networks, specifically macrocell-femtocell cooperation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a coalitional game, which falls under the category of cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). The paper also discusses throughput and delay, which are related to information theory, falling under the category of cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also mentions simulation results, which could fall under the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
